item_description:
(1) Sennheiser EW 100 G2 Receiver

(1) Sennheiser EW 100 G2 Receiver

  • Antennas and power supply included
  • Photos are representative of this item.
  • Compatible with lots 175 through 180.

Sennheiser EM100G2 Overview

  • The Sennheiser EM100G2 is a rack/table mountable wireless microphone receiver designed for use with the Sennheiser Evolution G2 series. The receiver is made of a durable metal enclosure and features a fully functional LED display. The 1/4" output connection provides a balanced or unbalanced (switchable) signal. Four preset memory locations can be reassigned to any of the 1280 available frequencies, within the 32MHz tuning range.

UHF Transmission

  • The Sennheiser Evolution series operates on UHF frequencies allowing longer range and few drop-outs and interference.

Flexible Frequency Options

  • The receiver is pre-configured with 4 preset channels, however, the channels can be reconfigured with any of the available 1280 frequencies within the 32MHz range.

Comprehensive Display

  • A comprehensive LED display provides channels and frequency information as well as battery life, usage time, signal status, and more.

Rugged Metal Design

  • Both transmitter and receiver feature a rugged, metal enclosure designed to withstand the rigors of road use and the elements. Its hyper-cardioid element rejects off-axis noise and reduces feedback caused by nearby speakers.
